WEBVTT

00:02.025 --> 00:03.827
Back away!

00:03.936 --> 00:05.496
We shouldn't even be here!
Without us,

00:05.569 --> 00:07.670
they have to surrender,
and we all go home.

00:07.849 --> 00:10.009
You really think you can
break that kind of devotion?

00:10.010 --> 00:11.312
Well, she's got faith.

00:11.418 --> 00:13.188
She's in love.
Those things are curable.

00:14.467 --> 00:15.886
Hopper, stay with me!

00:16.035 --> 00:18.331
Gil Langston, Captain.
Thank you for the pickup.

00:18.440 --> 00:19.960
- How's your man?
- Needs a hospital.

00:19.961 --> 00:21.440
We gotta leave right now!

00:23.027 --> 00:23.978
Gil!

00:29.618 --> 00:32.183
I need a place to keep my friend
until I can get him home.

00:32.945 --> 00:34.265
Your captain reneged on our deal.

00:34.550 --> 00:36.121
One of you must pay for his failure.

00:36.234 --> 00:37.274
I will let you choose who.

00:37.359 --> 00:38.559
Don't do this!
We had a deal!

00:38.560 --> 00:40.224
Okay, him. Take him.

00:40.374 --> 00:41.424
No! No, no, no, no!

00:41.522 --> 00:43.750
- Red, I'm sorry!
- Josh! Cortez!

00:48.723 --> 00:49.883
There's one more!

00:50.030 --> 00:52.148
No, there is not.
You were late.

00:52.477 --> 00:54.357
- He killed Red?
- What are you gonna do, Sam?

00:54.457 --> 00:55.817
We can't keep asking more of them.

00:55.932 --> 00:57.132
The one thing we have out here

00:57.133 --> 00:58.773
is our loyalty to each other.
That's it!

